  "detailed_description": "Inspired by the classic Sokoban games, Sticky Struggles adds its own unique gameplay mechanics. When you're located next to a block, it sticks to you, and the only way to let go of it is by placing it in the correct location! Are you ready for the challenge?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/1ce13f8d8e5dcec124952d5e80c0a3e5.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/1ce13f8d8e5dcec124952d5e80c0a3e5.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy a minimalist game world with relaxing music. No flashy visuals and loud sound effects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/ef63c762cd24122c4369b89209b42016.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/ef63c762cd24122c4369b89209b42016.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Play through 50 challenging levels. Once completed, you get instant access to 25 bonus levels!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/69f1c473af878267071ae2f064e0f876.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/69f1c473af878267071ae2f064e0f876.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>There are plenty of achievements to earn, can you collect them all?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/4de2c2c64903462e08aea59126c4775c.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/4de2c2c64903462e08aea59126c4775c.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>There are multiple ways to solve each level. Can you figure out how to solve it in the lowest amount of moves possible?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/c6210b4b1f031afaf9183901b3170d92.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/c6210b4b1f031afaf9183901b3170d92.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>You can easily toggle between 2D and 3D view.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/c517f7d1c7661b1fe04d2a1840111fa8.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=297 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Inspired by the classic Sokoban games, Sticky Struggles adds its own unique gameplay mechanics. When you're located next to a block, it sticks to you, and the only way to let go of it is by placing it in the correct location! Are you ready for the challenge?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/1ce13f8d8e5dcec124952d5e80c0a3e5.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/1ce13f8d8e5dcec124952d5e80c0a3e5.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy a minimalist game world with relaxing music. No flashy visuals and loud sound effects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/ef63c762cd24122c4369b89209b42016.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/ef63c762cd24122c4369b89209b42016.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Play through 50 challenging levels. Once completed, you get instant access to 25 bonus levels!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/69f1c473af878267071ae2f064e0f876.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/69f1c473af878267071ae2f064e0f876.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>There are plenty of achievements to earn, can you collect them all?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/4de2c2c64903462e08aea59126c4775c.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/4de2c2c64903462e08aea59126c4775c.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>There are multiple ways to solve each level. Can you figure out how to solve it in the lowest amount of moves possible?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/c6210b4b1f031afaf9183901b3170d92.poster.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/c6210b4b1f031afaf9183901b3170d92.webm?t=1748155124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>You can easily toggle between 2D and 3D view.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931070/extras/c517f7d1c7661b1fe04d2a1840111fa8.avif?t=1748155124\" width=616 height=297 /></span>",
